# Pipeline & Ops Rules

Read `.agent/skills/ops/SKILL.md` and `.agent/skills/data_integrity_guard/SKILL.md`.

## Data Integrity

- Atomic writes: `.tmp` → `rename()` for all parquet output
- Done markers: `filename.parquet.done` after successful processing
- Fail ledger: `fail_ledger.json` tracks deterministic failures
- Schema-first: validate on first file before bulk processing

## Deployment

- Deploy via `git push` only — no SCP
- Commit before deploy — no dirty-tree deployments
- Workers never push code (read-only pull model)
- Run `tools/env_verify.py --strict` after every sync

## Logging

- Use `omega_core/omega_log.py` for structured output
- Available levels: DEBUG, INFO, WARN, GUARDRAIL, ERROR, FATAL
- JSON mode: set `OMEGA_LOG_FORMAT=json`
